oai_dc:dc.dc:title: AFA Winter Meeting and IFCB Symposium Scheduled for February 11-15, [987
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: N/A, N/A
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: -If you will be attending the Jean Delacour IFCB Symposium in Hollywood from February 11 through 15, 1987 (which is also the AFA mid-year mini-convention), we have free color maps of the area to help you get around. These maps are provided courtesy of Mark Lacey, manager of Enterprise RentA-Car and include all of Los Angeles, Orange and Ventura counties, plus San Diego and Palm Springs and parts of Riverside and San Barnardino counties. Just write to the AFA home office and ask for the Enterprise Rent-A-Car map, but please send a self-addressed stamped envelope. These will also be available at the mini-convention. Many thanks, Mark!(The AFA board meeting is scheduled for February 11th. When registering for the symposium, please do not forget to write "AFA member" on your check and on the registration form.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: AFA Watchbird; Vol. 13 No. 5 (1986): OCT- NOV 1986; 38-39
